metadata.name: Steve Aoki // Valentino
metadata.description:
Strange Fashion - Spring Collection  
3264 Ã— 5824 Pixel

In the year twenty-fifty-two,  
Steve Aoki came into view,  
Dressed in Valentino's vibrant hue,  
A sight so stunning, it left us anew.

Electric blues and neon greens,  
In his outfit, a futuristic dream,  
The crowd gasped at the sight they've seen,  
A fashion icon, the likes of which we've never seen.

The beats he dropped were out of this world,  
His Valentino outfit, a perfect swirl,  
Of colors that danced and twirled,  
A fashion statement that left us all enthralled.

In the future, fashion knows no bounds,  
As we witness new styles come around,  
And Steve Aoki, with his Valentino's sound,  
Is a sight that will forever astound.
